e>   I MADE 16!!! YEAH!.....uh.....what do I kill now?</span><hr size=1> HEY! I just made level 16! WHOOO HOOOO! NEW PET! Ok, but anyways...what now? I have nice armor, and items, decent pp, all I need now is a decent area to break into the next level of being a mage....DAMN! I have NO idea where to go, I've almost exhusted the possiblities of Black Burrow and the Tundra, If ANYONE has a good spot they did well in PLEASE post where, what to kill and what pet you found to beat on stuff with best! THANKS!  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/unefariusgnome.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nefarius Gnome</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Conjurer</span><br>  Posts: 114<br> <font color=#333333>(10/5/00 6:21:06 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm41.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: I MADE 16!!! YEAH!.....uh.....what do I kill now?</span><hr size=1> You can do the gargoyles in OOT. Great exp and money (eyes go for about 8pp each). The gargoyles are easy to pull solo. You may need to kill skeleton placeholders to get the gargoyles to spawn. Just watch out for the spectres. <p><p><font face="Arial" COLOR="blue" size="2"><b>Nefarius Frobozz</b><br>Devout Agnostic Gnome Magician of the 31st Trial<i><br>Terris-Thule<br></i></p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=balthemal>Balthemal</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 76<br> <font color=#333333>(7/19/01 1:55:33 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm41.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=le