Unrest (soloing yard stuff or grouped)<br>
LOIO (get into a mill group)<br>
EK, SK (endless stuff to kill here, the problem is finding it....get a tracker partner)<br>
Najena (Yes, you can actually hunt in this zone for exp)<br>
Upper Guk (Ditto)<br>
Everfrost (Plenty of blues to solo here.....)<br>
The Warrens (Never been there, but at 16 you should be able to hunt most things for exp here)<br>
<br>
Some others that I'm forgetting.......<br>
/shrug <br>
