As far as the Warrens go, the majority of stuff that will be blue/even to you at 16 will be the majority of the named kobolds... The Prince, King, some of the littler guys like the Foodmaster and Smith...  The only problem is, the kobolds are VERY VERY social.  Hence, you have to clear out multiple greens to get to the expable mobs.  I tried soloing in here with my 15 mage and kept getting roasted by greenie adds.  Also tried duoing in here with a 15 necro and got roasted by greenie adds.  *sigh*<br>
